values:
Ok, I'm dead.
I suck at writing journals/diaries/blogs.
Bye im_in_distress.
You were the only one who saw my journal.
^^

Aw. I haven't written in 2 weeks.
Ohwell.
I'm not in a mood of writing right now either.
But I'm just updating to show that I'm still alive.

I want to improve my English. My vocabulary is too small and my entries are so limited, because I just don't know how to express myself. And it would be so boring if I'd write in Estonian, 'cause then nobody but Estonian people could understand me and my English skill would stay as it is right now. And that would suck!
We're having our school's Christmas party tonight. I hope it will be cool. They promised not to play this damn club music. And that makes me happy, 'cause my God, I hate that crap. Tonight's party's style is retro. But I have anything to wear.. :/ So I'll be boring and wear my everyday clothes. Go Mari, yay. But I wish Karl could come too... MyDreamGuy. Lol. :P But he has to go to get his report card. The lad plays drums. * Adooooooores *. I just HAVE to tell him how I feel about him. I mean, what have I got to loose? I don't think it would rue our friendship. It didn't rue it in spring. But now it's winter and I must try again. Or what do you think? Omg, what would I do without Allan and Alfi? :P Allan is like, giving me hope all the time. And Alfi encourages me to tell. * Thanks them. *
